(1) Gutters
------------
==> Gutters are the padding between your columns, used to responsively space and align content in the Bootstrap grid system.


(2) Horizontal Gutters (gx-[0-5])
-----------------------

    <div class="container px-4">
      <div class="row gx-5">
        <div class="col-6">
          <div class="p-3 border bg-light">Custom column padding</div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-6">
          <div class="p-3 border bg-light">Custom column padding</div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-6">
          <div class="p-3 border bg-light">Custom column padding</div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-5">
          <div class="p-3 border bg-light">Custom column padding</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    
(3) Vertical Gutters (gy-[0-5])
----------------------

    <div class="container px-4">
      <div class="row gx-5 gy-5">
        <div class="col-6">
          <div class="p-3 border bg-light">Custom column padding</div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-6">
          <div class="p-3 border bg-light">Custom column padding</div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-6">
          <div class="p-3 border bg-light">Custom column padding</div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-5">
          <div class="p-3 border bg-light">Custom column padding</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    
(4) Horizontal & vertical Gutters
----------------------------------

    <div class="container px-4">
      <div class="row g-5">
        <div class="col-6">
          <div class="p-3 border bg-light">Custom column padding</div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-6">
          <div class="p-3 border bg-light">Custom column padding</div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-6">
          <div class="p-3 border bg-light">Custom column padding</div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-5">
          <div class="p-3 border bg-light">Custom column padding</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    
(5) Row Columns Gutters (g-[0-5])
------------------------

    <div class="container px-4">
      <div class="row row-cols-2 g-2 g-lg-5">
        <div class="col">
          <div class="p-3 border bg-light">Custom column padding</div>
        </div>
        <div class="col">
          <div class="p-3 border bg-light">Custom column padding</div>
        </div>
        <div class="col">
          <div class="p-3 border bg-light">Custom column padding</div>
        </div>
        <div class="col">
          <div class="p-3 border bg-light">Custom column padding</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    
(6) No Gutters [removes the negative margins from .row and the horizontal padding from all immediate children columns]
---------------

    <div class="container">
      <div class="row g-0">
        <div class="col">
          <div class="p-3 border bg-light">Custom column padding</div>
        </div>
        <div class="col">
          <div class="p-3 border bg-light">Custom column padding</div>
        </div>
        <div class="col">
          <div class="p-3 border bg-light">Custom column padding</div>
        </div>
        <div class="col">
          <div class="p-3 border bg-light">Custom column padding</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
